<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 ạkẖtrt tfdy ḥyạty wbạ̉smy ʿrftny
 mn ṭyn ạlḥmạ̉ẗ rfʿtny ( wbrwḥk msḥtny )
 bạdylk ạ̉ḥlạmy bạdylk ạlwạny
 ạ̉fkạry ạlḥạny bạdylk ( kl kyạny )
 ʿynyk yạrby ʿly btsẖjʿny wtḥbny
 wrwḥk sạkn fy ( wạydyk btḍmny )
 qlby bdyk hdyẗ wʿyny ʿly̱ ṭwl ʿlyk
 wmwạhby lyk yạ fạdy ( tmjdk tʿlyk )</lyrics>
<title>ạkẖtrt tfdy ḥyạty</title>
<author>krystyn nẓmy, krystyn nẓmy</author>
